title: 608 25th St. 3BR Single Family Home $2200 1/2 off Aug. rent
posting_body: ['2 story 3BR 1.25BA home available 8/1 in the heart of Whittier!', 'Beautiful, classic woodwork throughout, wood floors, buffet,  original light fixtures, big basement with laundry and lots of storage, small front porch, and sunroom off the living room.', 'The building has a newer hot water boiler with in-floor heating and new, energy efficient windows.', 'Tenant provides snow removal for steps and small front sidewalk and lawncare for a very small front yard.', 'Water, sewer, and trash are included in the rent.', 'Tenant pays electric, gas, phone, cable, internet.', 'The house is close to The Wedge, public transportation, parks, playgrounds, lakes, MIA, theaters, restaurants.', 'Cats okay!', 'Parking is on the street.', 'No smoking building.', "Deposit typically equals 1 month's rent.", '20 application fee per adult to obtain credit and criminal background info.', 'Good rental references required.', 'Income requirement 3X the monthly rent.', 'Please email for an appointment.', 'When you do include some dates / times that work for you.', 'Thanks!']
